  - name: About This Dashboard
    type: text
    title_text: About This Dashboard
    body_text: |-
      This dashboard is an enhanced version of 'Business Pulse - Basic visualization examples'.

      This dashboard adds these features
      <br>- Info about the Users' First Orders
      <br>- Product specific info
      <br>- Geographic visuals


      <details><summary>+ Other notes</summary>
      - This Dashboard shows only Valid items (Items that were not cancelled or returned)
      <br>- ‘New Users’ only counts users with any valid orders meeting the filter criteria.
      <br>- INTERACTIVITY REMINDER: Click field values to drill down to more detail.
      <br><br>
      </details>
    row: 0
    col: 0
    width: 12
    height: 5
    tab_name: ''
